description: This file defines a data model for movie scripts using Pydantic, and sets up an agent with a language model to generate movie scripts based on prompts.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script, including fields for name, setting, ending, genre, characters, and storyline.

methods.name: agent.print_response
methods.description: Method to generate and print a response from the agent based on a prompt.
